item.title: CVE-2023-6271|2024-01-01T14:18:55.067Z -- unknown -- backup%20migration
item.description: The Backup Migration WordPress plugin before 1.3.6 stores in-progress backups information in easy to find, publicly-accessible files, which may allow attackers monitoring those to leak sensitive information from the site's backups.
